{
  "stem": "1473.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I kept saying, gee, it's just like in this Rita Hayworth movie, or in that Cary Grant movie.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Don't forget, in Switzerland we saw American movies.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was just like in the movies, except worse, because of the heat.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had never experienced such heat and humidity.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my uncle Heini kept saying, we thought you had a nervous tick, because you constantly went like this.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I thought-- I was unaware of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I thought by going like this, I could-- it was a heat wave.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was the 4th of July heat, humid-- the typical thing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I lived with-- my cousin's brother was still in the army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they lived in a furnished apartment on West 98th Street-- my cousin.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, I first went to Kingston, New York, where my aunt lived.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My aunt-- I had my father's older sister wanted me to stay with them in Kingston, New York, where they had come in 1941, I believe, before the war.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there these relatives who didn't send the affidavit lived, in great luxury.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I just found Kingston dreadful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I wanted to go to work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I wanted to go to work in New York.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was trained.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was trained in commercial and sort of international subjects.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had the diploma of that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I went to interview with a local branch of a French bank.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was immediately hired.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the custom was not to be paid when you were an apprentice, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But when they offered me $35 a week, I thought I was just about very rich.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And everybody thought so, too, that for someone who-- who spoke no English to get $35 a week was--",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
